dc_description_s: This data layer represents trails for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NSt_Croix_Trails_2018.gdbN. [A trail or path used for walking, cycling, hiking or other form of non-vehicular transportation. In some cases, other forms of motorized transportation may be permitted on a regular or seasonal basis.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: St. Croix County Land Use, Planning and Development
